'''Gadrin''' is one of the three [[Dwarf (Mining Guild)|dwarves]] who guard the [[Mining Guild]] in the south-eastern area of [[Falador]], next to the ladders that lead into the guild. He sells the [[Mining cape]] and [[Mining hood|hood]] to those who have achieved 99 [[Mining]].

==Stock==
Note: If a player has multiple [[Skill mastery|99s]], they will receive the trimmed variant of the cape instead.
